casebody.data:
No. 397,

Mise.

Prendez v. Craven, Warden. Thomas G. Lynch, Attorney General of California, Doris H. Maier, Assistant Attorney General, and Edward A. Hinz, Jr., Deputy Attorney General, for respondent.

C. A. 9th Cir. Certiorari denied. Mr. Justice Brennan and Mr. Justice Stewart are of the opinion that cer-tiorari should be granted, the judgment vacated, and the case remanded for further consideration in light of Peyton v. Rowe, 391 U. S. 54.
